21st-century-blues-album-review" target="_blank" rel="noopener">recently said</a> that such bold and brave declarations wouldn&#39;t have been released had she still been signed to a major label. Granted her creative independence, though, the hard-fought &#39;My 21st Century Blues&#39; is unequivocally RAYE from start to finish.”</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-responds-to-not-being-nominated-for-2024-grammys-3538435">RAYE responds to not being nominated for 2024 Grammys</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
